<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <HEAD>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
     <TITLE>FIND</TITLE>
   </HEAD>
   <BODY>
     <div class="w3-top">
      <div class="w3-bar w3-dark-grey">
        <a href="/home" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">홈</ a>
        <a href="/insert" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">생성</a>
        <a href="/edit" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">수정</a>
        <a href="/del" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">삭제</a>
<!--     <a href="/find" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">찾기</a>  -->
        <a href="/list" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">명단</a>
      </div>
     </div>
     <br><br>
     <div class="w3-header w3-center">
       <h2>회원정보검색</h2>
     </div>
     <div class="w3-table w3-cyan w3-center">
       <FORM METHOD="POST">
         <div class="w3-center w3-text-white"><h3>검색할 회원 이름을 입력하세요</h3></div>
         <TABLE align="center">
           <TR>
             <TD><LABEL>회원의 이름</LABEL></TD>
             <TD><INPUT TYPE="TEXT" NAME="name"/></TD>
           </TR>
           <tr>
             <td></td><td><input type="submit" value="찾 기" class="w3-button w3-round-xxlarge w3-purple w3-block"/></td>
           </tr>
           <tr></tr>
         </TABLE>
       </FORM>
     </div>
     <div class="w3-margin w3-text-purple w3-center">
       <p>회원이름은 공백문자를 포함, 가입한 회원이름과 동일하게 입력해주세요.</p>
     </div>

     <table class="w3-table-all">
       <thead>
         <tr class="w3-blue">
           <th>번호</th><th>성 명</th><th>거주지</th>
         </tr>
       </thead>
        <% data.forEach(function(user) { %>
        <%# // 필드명이 대문자이면 ejsHTML문서에서도 대문자(ID, NAME, REGION)여야 함 %>
        <tr>
          <td>[<%= user.id %>]</td>
          <td><%= user.name %></td>
          <td><%= user.region %></td>
        </tr>
       <% }) %>
     </table>
   </BODY>
 </HTML>
